abstract: Baseball Roundup; Detroit Tigers defeat Oakland Athletics, 7-3; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Zimmermann had his streak of scoreless innings end before he reached 25, but Miguel Cabrera hit two home runs to propel Detroit past Oakland.

headline.main: Tigers Win, but Jordan Zimmermann Yields Run, Ending a Streak
headline.print_headline: Tigers Win, but Their Starter Yields Run, Ending a Streak
